**Syntactic Analysis** In this process, the source file is parsed into an abstract syntax tree (AST). The syntactic role of*s*(e.g., name, attribute access, or call expression) determines the subsequent resolution strategy. For attribute expressions*a.b*, Pyright treats *a*as a receiver expression whose type must be inferred prior to member lookup. 

